==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exogamy
<hw>Ex*og"a*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The custom, or
tribal law, which prohibits marriage between members of the same tribe;
marriage outside of the tribe; -- opposed to
<contr>endogamy</contr>.</def> <rj><au>Lubbock.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exogen</ent>⟦br⟧
